{"tid":1784060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傭人之國】6.8級地震！4死！三層超市倒塌！","createTime":"2019-12-15T11:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T07:42:56.000Z","uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5be935484b21fe9ede0ab481f38188881886db2f","tid":1784060,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"菲律賓達沃市周日發生黎克特制6.8級地震，目前已增至4死，另有24人受傷。地震發生時，總統杜特爾特亦身處達沃市，但他與家人都未受傷。<br />\n<br />\n地震震央位於達沃市西南61公里的棉蘭老島，震源深渡28公里。帕達達（Padada）一棟3層樓的超級市場倒塌，至少3人死亡，救援人員從倒榻大樓中救出6人，相信仍有不少人被埋在瓦礫下。"},{"pid":"da8a72b9857032a2816523ff2d0d271a89cf5bbf","tid":1784060,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b993da56c8ea27433380bf700e547c0f436987e0","tid":1784060,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e261b85dc092243c243ecb6ddf05a28d92020250","tid":1784060,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c3dd51233a28bdfd6052858a36537a2d7fcb04","tid":1784060,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"菲律賓&gt;支那"},{"pid":"5ecc785de51cd70d6058f728c0f23231f3ec7503","tid":1784060,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}